              <li>No credit will be given for this course unless both GEOG 492D1 and GEOG 492D2 are successfully completed in consecutive terms</li>
            </ul>
      </div>

  </div> <!-- /.node -->
              </div>
            </div>
          </li>
                </ul>
      
      
                <h4>Remaining Geography</h4>

    
              <p>6-9 credits from a coherent set of Geography (GEOG) courses approved by the Program Adviser.  Including a field course is desirable.</p>
    
      
      
            </div>

    
  
